10:56.758 --> 10:59.160
Hello. I'm Linda.

10:59.161 --> 11:02.396
♪ And I want you to clean your room ♪

11:02.397 --> 11:04.632
♪ So I'm singing
this song. ♪

11:04.633 --> 11:08.486
♪ But I'm not gonna clean
my room, la-la la-la la-la. ♪

11:08.487 --> 11:10.788
No-no-no-no.
No singing. Wha...?

11:10.789 --> 11:12.990
I'm doing you.
That's why I'm singing.

11:12.991 --> 11:15.793
You're doing me, so you don't sing.
Oh, like I'm not gonna sing!

11:15.794 --> 11:18.496
♪ Oh, you better clean your room ♪
♪ I will never clean my room ♪

11:18.497 --> 11:20.848
♪ 'Cause I'm singing this song ♪
♪ 'Cause I'm so rebellious! ♪

11:20.849 --> 11:23.918
♪ And you're gonna clean your room! ♪
♪ No, I'm not gonna stop! ♪

11:23.919 --> 11:26.320
Okay, you two are done.
Big hand for Linda and Louise.

11:26.321 --> 11:27.938
Please sit down.
Great. You blew it.

11:27.973 --> 11:30.174
<i>I</i> blew it? You gave me
nothing out there!

11:30.175 --> 11:32.777
Well, nothing is what
you're getting paid for that!

11:32.811 --> 11:34.779
Whoa. Time out. Linda,
have you been paying

11:34.780 --> 11:37.014
your daughter to be here?
I'm sorry, Dakota,

11:37.015 --> 11:39.316
but it's the only way she'd do it.

11:39.317 --> 11:40.491
I'm a terrible mother.

11:40.519 --> 11:43.287
Oh, Linda, you really, really are.

11:43.321 --> 11:44.538
Everybody, everybody, listen, okay?

11:44.539 --> 11:46.497
Linda is a good mother.
Mwa.

11:46.508 --> 11:48.642
Because she did it out of love.

11:48.643 --> 11:50.778
And that puts you in the running for

11:50.779 --> 11:53.481
the Most Valuable Mommy award...
the MVM, everybody...

11:53.482 --> 11:55.999
which I give out at the end of the day.

11:56.000 --> 11:57.749
- All right!
- MVM!

11:57.750 --> 11:58.986
Pshh...

11:58.987 --> 12:01.055
And as for you, I don't feel like

12:01.056 --> 12:02.805
you're taking Modo Time seriously.

12:02.824 --> 12:04.307
Oh, no, not at all.

12:04.326 --> 12:06.142
And that makes me feel
negatively towards you.

12:06.161 --> 12:08.028
Well, maybe this will
help clear things up.

12:08.029 --> 12:10.798
Here's your seminar.
See it?

12:10.799 --> 12:12.983
It's so cute and nice
in my hand, and...

12:14.352 --> 12:16.170
Did you just fart on my seminar?

12:16.171 --> 12:17.505
Ye, me, too!

12:17.506 --> 12:18.806
Okay, that's... that's fine.

12:18.807 --> 12:20.823
I think I know what we need to do here.

12:21.860 --> 12:23.961
Hey! Watch it!
Get off me!

12:23.995 --> 12:26.564
You two will stay in there
until you're ready

12:26.565 --> 12:28.232
to engage in this experience!

12:28.233 --> 12:29.600
Oh, almost forgot.

12:29.601 --> 12:31.869
Oh, God.
What is that?

12:31.870 --> 12:33.771
It's <i>Freaky Friday</i> on a loop.

12:33.772 --> 12:36.056
Mom, you're old.
And you're young!

12:36.057 --> 12:38.109
Wouldn't it be crazy
if we switched bodies?

12:38.110 --> 12:39.967
No...!

12:42.047 --> 12:43.680
No...!

12:45.417 --> 12:46.617
Oh-hoo-hoo!

12:49.072 --> 12:51.485
Oh, no, we switched bodies!

12:51.486 --> 12:53.120
What a crazy journey we are on.

12:53.121 --> 12:55.489
The logic of this movie
is very unsettling!

12:55.490 --> 12:57.741
You can't do this, you monsters!

12:57.776 --> 12:59.510
All right, well,
why don't you two pair up

12:59.511 --> 13:00.978
now that your children are locked away?

13:01.012 --> 13:03.614
Of course, Dakota.
Come on, Cynthia.

13:03.615 --> 13:06.083
Let's you and me learn
some mommy skills together.

13:06.084 --> 13:07.484
I'd like that, Linda.

13:07.485 --> 13:09.053
And don't forget about

13:09.087 --> 13:10.988
that Most Valuable Mommy
award, everybody.

13:10.989 --> 13:12.623
It's a beautiful sash.

13:12.657 --> 13:13.991
- Huh. Huh.
- Hmm.

13:13.992 --> 13:15.676
- Hmm.
- Ah.

13:15.677 --> 13:18.178
I want that sash.
Over my dead body.

13:18.179 --> 13:20.447
I want that sash.
I love sashes.

13:22.050 --> 13:24.134
My legs are so free.

13:24.135 --> 13:26.019
Mmm. So that's what
air feels like.

13:26.054 --> 13:27.687
It's nice.

13:27.688 --> 13:29.206
Yeah, these pants feel incredible.

13:29.207 --> 13:30.958
Why don't all men do this?

13:30.959 --> 13:33.043
Hmph!
Gene, why are you making noises?

13:33.044 --> 13:34.528
They're my
jealousy noises! Ugh!

13:34.529 --> 13:35.879
What are you saying?

13:35.880 --> 13:38.165
I want to wax my legs, too!

13:38.166 --> 13:39.466
These ones right here!

13:39.467 --> 13:41.335
You don't even have leg hair.

13:41.336 --> 13:43.036
Tell that to my heart!

13:43.071 --> 13:44.888
Hold on, everybody.
We're making a U-turn.

13:44.889 --> 13:46.657
All right!

13:46.691 --> 13:49.810
Ow!
Gentle touch, Cynthia.

13:49.811 --> 13:51.345
A mother's gentle touch.

13:51.346 --> 13:53.547
I'm so sorry.

13:53.548 --> 13:55.516
You know, Dakota, when
I braid Louise's hair,

13:55.517 --> 13:58.051
I sing her a song.
Ah, yes, please.

13:58.086 --> 14:01.321
♪ Here goes the hair and
there goes the hair ♪ Ah...

14:01.322 --> 14:03.490
♪ And where is Harry Truman?

14:03.491 --> 14:06.059
♪ He's dead in the ground,
he's dead in the ground ♪

14:06.060 --> 14:09.146
♪ He's dead, dead,
dead... ♪ Ow! Ow!

14:09.180 --> 14:10.547
Well we switched bodies again,

14:10.548 --> 14:13.050
and everything's back to normal.

14:13.051 --> 14:14.685
I finally understand you, Mom.

14:14.686 --> 14:16.520
<i>Freaky Friday's</i> getting to me, man.

14:16.521 --> 14:18.088
They really understand each other!

14:18.089 --> 14:19.356
You pull yourself together.

14:19.357 --> 14:21.074
We got to get out of here.

14:21.075 --> 14:23.694
They just had to see things
from each other's perspective.

14:23.695 --> 14:25.245
Logan, come on!
We got to think!

14:25.246 --> 14:27.247
Walk a mile in each other's shoes...

14:27.248 --> 14:29.399
Oh, I swear to God,
if you keep talking,

14:29.400 --> 14:31.101
I'm gonna gut-punch you!

14:31.102 --> 14:33.670
It's a beautiful story
of love and acceptance.

14:33.671 --> 14:34.905
Oh, my stomach!

14:34.906 --> 14:36.590
Wait a minute.
That's it!

14:36.624 --> 14:39.126
Wow. See?
What'd I tell you?

14:39.127 --> 14:40.194
That is smooth.

14:40.195 --> 14:41.378
Whoa, whoa, Teddy.

14:41.379 --> 14:43.213
What, a little high up on the leg?

14:43.214 --> 14:44.548
- Yeah.
- Sorry.

14:44.549 --> 14:45.783
There's a stop sign right here.

14:45.784 --> 14:47.117
Now feel mine.
And mine.

14:47.118 --> 14:48.439
No, Teddy, don't touch their legs.

14:48.453 --> 14:50.187
Look at this.
Whoa!

14:50.221 --> 14:52.189
You could wash a pan with that.

14:52.223 --> 14:54.424
Hey, maybe I'll shoot over
there and get what you got.

14:54.425 --> 14:55.959
Yeah.
Nah, on second thought,

14:55.960 --> 14:57.594
I couldn't get rid
of these little guys.

14:57.595 --> 14:59.096
They're my little furry friends.

14:59.097 --> 15:01.131
Don't listen to him.
You're an embarrassment!

15:01.132 --> 15:03.100
No, don't listen to him.
You're all right.

15:03.134 --> 15:05.269
Furry little... friends?

15:07.205 --> 15:09.006
This is fun! Higher, Tina!

15:09.040 --> 15:11.708
Higher!

