15:27.792 --> 15:31.094
Watch out for that bear!
Whoo! Here comes a puma!

15:32.664 --> 15:33.964
- Mommy! Mommy!
- Mommy!

15:33.965 --> 15:35.766
Did you hear that, everybody?

15:35.767 --> 15:37.885
They're coming around.
The Uter-Room is working!

15:37.919 --> 15:41.738
Oh, that umbilical soup
got me, Mom. Got me real bad.

15:41.739 --> 15:43.006
Rub my tummy?

15:43.007 --> 15:44.508
Mine, too.

15:44.509 --> 15:46.677
Oh, my poor baby.

15:48.079 --> 15:49.680
It's wonderful.

15:49.681 --> 15:52.683
A mother's instinct
at its most primal level!

15:52.684 --> 15:54.418
Come, other mothers, come and see!

15:54.452 --> 15:56.920
Mommy's gonna make you all better.

15:56.921 --> 15:59.189
Well, this mommy's gonna
make you all better first.

16:00.859 --> 16:02.843
Now! Ha!

16:02.844 --> 16:05.178
What the hell's going on?
Uh, what are... what are you doing?

16:05.213 --> 16:07.347
You fell for the oldest trick
in the book.

16:07.348 --> 16:09.683
The fake tummy ache!
The old belly bluff.

16:09.717 --> 16:10.817
Oh, the belly bluff!

16:10.852 --> 16:12.119
Now, if you'll excuse us,

16:12.120 --> 16:13.520
us girls...

16:13.521 --> 16:15.155
Sorry. Ladies...
Thank you.

16:15.156 --> 16:17.057
Are going to play laser tag.
Whoo-hoo!

16:17.058 --> 16:20.491
Oh, I hope those lasers
hit you right in the butt!

16:24.962 --> 16:26.430
Come on, you!

16:26.431 --> 16:27.697
Damn these delicate shoulders!

16:27.698 --> 16:29.266
Let me try.

16:30.818 --> 16:33.086
Where'd you learn how
to break down a door,

16:33.087 --> 16:34.337
Girl Scout camp?
Move it.

16:40.478 --> 16:42.429
No covering your sensors.

16:42.430 --> 16:44.531
No climbing on the barriers.

16:44.532 --> 16:48.018
And no physical contact of any kind.

16:48.052 --> 16:49.719
Well, agree to disagree.

16:49.720 --> 16:53.023
I feel kind of bad about
locking our moms in that room.

16:54.025 --> 16:55.826
Ah, hey!

16:55.860 --> 16:57.294
<i>I killed them.</i>

16:57.328 --> 16:58.562
I killed them all.

16:58.563 --> 16:59.729
Tina, what...
what's wrong?

16:59.730 --> 17:01.331
I killed my friendly leg hairs.

17:01.332 --> 17:03.834
Um... oh.
Well, they'll grow back.

17:03.835 --> 17:05.635
It's not just that.

17:05.670 --> 17:07.204
I did it 'cause I was worried

17:07.204 --> 17:09.005
about what those girls
would think of me.

17:09.006 --> 17:10.840
I'm a sheep!
A hairless sheep!

17:10.875 --> 17:12.509
So you gave in to peer pressure.

17:12.510 --> 17:13.907
It happens to everybody.

17:13.911 --> 17:16.195
I mean, why do you think
I wear these shoes?

17:16.196 --> 17:18.047
'Cause you don't care
what you look like?

17:18.048 --> 17:19.566
What? No.
'Cause I... No.

17:19.567 --> 17:21.367
'Cause I saw some other
chefs wearing them

17:21.368 --> 17:22.836
and I thought they were cool.

17:22.837 --> 17:23.970
Don't you think?

17:23.971 --> 17:25.070
Yeah, yeah.

17:25.071 --> 17:26.506
What do you mean?

17:26.507 --> 17:28.191
I think they're...
Yeah, they're cool.

17:28.192 --> 17:30.060
Um... okay. Well, because
if they don't look...

17:30.061 --> 17:32.662
if they look stupid, I won't wear them.

17:32.663 --> 17:34.498
No, they... Yeah.
Forget it. Listen.

17:34.532 --> 17:36.433
Leg hair or no leg hair,
you're still Tina,

17:36.434 --> 17:38.268
and when it comes
to the important stuff,

17:38.269 --> 17:39.769
you'll make the right choice.

17:39.770 --> 17:41.204
Gene, put some pants on.

17:41.205 --> 17:42.305
- No!
- Ugh.

17:44.876 --> 17:46.190
What the hell?

17:46.210 --> 17:47.427
How'd you get out?

17:47.428 --> 17:49.262
I busted through the door.

17:49.263 --> 17:51.331
Um, <i>we</i> busted through the door.

17:51.332 --> 17:53.266
Fine. My shoulder
and Cynthia's left boob.

17:53.267 --> 17:55.502
All right, everybody.
Fun's over.

17:55.503 --> 17:57.201
Now, let's get back on Modo Time.

17:57.205 --> 17:58.889
Oh, no freaking way!

17:58.923 --> 18:01.725
You are coming back
to the Nurture Center right now!

18:01.726 --> 18:03.927
You're in big trouble,
Logan Berry Bush.

18:03.928 --> 18:04.928
Huh?

18:04.929 --> 18:06.213
Logan Berry Bush?

18:06.214 --> 18:07.614
We didn't think it through.

18:07.615 --> 18:08.748
Okay, everybody, calm down.

18:08.749 --> 18:10.350
Now, how do we get down there?

18:10.351 --> 18:12.736
No one goes in without
a vest and a laser gun.

18:12.737 --> 18:13.937
Well, that's not happening.

18:13.938 --> 18:15.472
I'll go down there!
Linda, no!

18:15.473 --> 18:16.740
Laser tag goes against

18:16.741 --> 18:18.742
everything we've been working on.

18:18.743 --> 18:20.043
And besides...
you're mothers.

18:20.044 --> 18:22.312
Uh-huh.
Where's mommy's gun?!

18:22.313 --> 18:23.914
So, welcome to the war.

18:23.915 --> 18:25.549
Okay, first, uh...
let's just try

18:25.550 --> 18:27.217
to create a dialogue, and we'll...

18:30.972 --> 18:32.789
You're gonna get it, Miss Missy!

18:32.807 --> 18:35.859
Why don't you let your gun
do the talking, blabbermouth!

18:35.893 --> 18:37.494
Blabbermouth?

18:44.785 --> 18:46.086
Linda, this isn't right!

18:46.120 --> 18:47.938
Feels pretty good to me!

18:47.972 --> 18:49.973
I am ordering you to put down your gun

18:49.974 --> 18:51.808
and go cradle your daughter!

18:51.809 --> 18:53.527
No! I'm gonna shoot her instead!

18:53.578 --> 18:55.111
Ha! Gotcha!

18:55.146 --> 18:57.514
I gave you that one!
Nah!

18:57.515 --> 18:59.082
This is seriously hurting your chances

18:59.083 --> 19:00.584
of receiving the MVM award!

19:00.618 --> 19:02.736
Maybe I should give
the sash to Cynthia, huh?

19:02.737 --> 19:04.304
Die, Logan!

19:04.628 --> 19:06.729
Oh-whoa-whoa-whoa,
seriously? I'm the MVM?

19:06.764 --> 19:08.850
What?! The sash! Oh!

19:08.908 --> 19:10.775
That's for kidnapping me!

19:10.810 --> 19:12.543
Ooh! Aah!

19:12.578 --> 19:14.912
And that's for taking me
to <i>The Momgina Monologues!</i>

19:14.946 --> 19:17.447
You almost killed your mother.
I hope you're happy.

19:17.481 --> 19:19.249
I am.
Any last words?

19:19.283 --> 19:21.785
Yes. I just wish...

19:21.820 --> 19:24.464
I just wish you liked me, that's all.

19:24.584 --> 19:26.551
But I guess you never will,
so go ahead,

19:26.586 --> 19:27.748
put me out of my misery.

19:27.868 --> 19:30.279
Is this all 'cause you think
I don't like you?

19:30.399 --> 19:33.808
Go on. Just do it. Just go.
Take me out. Go ahead.

19:34.153 --> 19:37.810
Mom, I guess I've been
kind of a "B" word today.

19:37.930 --> 19:40.999
You have. But I came on
a little strong.

19:41.033 --> 19:42.601
I'm sorr...

19:42.635 --> 19:45.571
You! You ruined my beautiful
seminar, you little brat!

19:45.605 --> 19:47.572
And now you're gonna pay!

19:47.606 --> 19:50.207
Aah!
No! My baby!

19:50.242 --> 19:52.276
Suck on this soup tube, Dakota!

19:52.310 --> 19:54.245
It's laser-flavored!

19:54.365 --> 19:56.647
Mom, nice!

20:00.252 --> 20:01.753
Look north, Dakota.

20:01.787 --> 20:03.521
Whoa, Mom, amazing!

20:03.555 --> 20:05.022
Make my day!

20:05.056 --> 20:06.857
No, no, better before.

20:06.892 --> 20:08.425
Wait, wait. Hold on.

20:10.295 --> 20:11.528
Hey, get off the equipment!

20:11.562 --> 20:12.469
Oh, shove it!

20:12.589 --> 20:14.265
I'm bonding with my daughter!

20:14.299 --> 20:16.233
Yeah, we're bonding here!

20:17.668 --> 20:19.403
Best therapy ever.

20:19.437 --> 20:21.771
You should have seen the
way Mom took down Dakota.

20:21.805 --> 20:23.306
Phenomimom, my ass.

20:23.340 --> 20:25.345
My ass, too!
Up high!

20:25.465 --> 20:26.938
Yeah, that my girl!

20:27.058 --> 20:28.577
Quit scratching, you two.

20:28.612 --> 20:29.866
Can't help it.
It itches.

20:29.986 --> 20:31.580
Yeah, mine, too.
Switch?

20:31.615 --> 20:32.338
Okay.

20:33.869 --> 20:35.750
Come on.
Scratch like a man!

20:35.870 --> 20:36.718
Give it to me!

20:36.752 --> 20:38.553
Tina, I'm sorry I wasn't there

20:38.587 --> 20:40.122
to give you your first shave.

20:40.156 --> 20:42.925
It's okay.
I regretted it anyway.

20:42.959 --> 20:45.327
But it was fun going
to the waxing salon with Dad.

20:45.361 --> 20:46.594
He's a screamer.

20:46.629 --> 20:48.630
Ow, Gene!
Not so hard!

20:48.664 --> 20:51.161
Aw, man! Your day sounds better.
What?

20:51.281 --> 20:53.801
I want to go shave my legs
with Dad and then regret it.

20:53.835 --> 20:55.636
Yeah, let's make all the same mistakes

20:55.670 --> 20:56.971
with Dad again tomorrow!

20:57.005 --> 20:58.272
Okay.
Yay, Dad.

20:58.307 --> 20:59.840
Oh, screw all of you.

20:59.874 --> 21:01.605
Ah, Mom.
Come here.

